snippet.title: Hot Wheels Custom Car Designer: PC Games
snippet.description: Build your dream Hot Wheels car. Print trophies and awards. Make your own drivers licence and plates! Write your own newspaper and create traffic tickets. Another great old game for old school windows PCs!
